dates explained above.  As with <A HREF="nrx12.htm#Table9.1">Table 9.1</A> of
<B>PE/NRX/12</B>, which it supersedes, the table excludes interest and
contingencies.  The projected outlay to first  waste emplacement is &#163;1820
million at 1995 prices, which is a net reduction of &#163;64 million on the
previous projection.  The net reduction can be broken down as follows:
