of additional expenditure during the RCF programme.  To help with that matter, a
classification of expenditure estimates is given in <A HREF="#Table4.2">Table
4.2</A> below.  For completeness that table covers the whole of Nirex's planned
activities - not simply those associated with the RCF.
</P>
