<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>Royal Society Study Group Report on the Science of Radioactive Waste
Disposal: Initial Nirex Response</P></BLOCKQUOTE></TD>
<TD></TD></TR></TABLE>
<P></P>
<TABLE BORDER="BORDER">
