<TD><FONT SIZE="-1">3-D Seismic reflection surveys</FONT></TD>
<TD><FONT SIZE="-1">Interpretation of the trial 3-D seismic survey is
proceeding. If this technique is shown to permit enhancement of the existing
geological model of the PRZ an evaluation will be made of the potential value of
extending the survey area to provide additional information on the geological
structure and rock properties at depth in a wider area.</FONT></TD>
<TD><FONT SIZE="-1">Ongoing.</FONT></TD>
<TD><FONT SIZE="-1">Potentially part of the RCF science programme to enhance
the existing geological model which is to be validated in the RCF.</FONT></TD></TR>
<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">
