<P><A NAME="TA11"></A><B>Table A.11:  Details Of Groundwater Pressure
Monitoring System</B></P>
<TABLE BORDER="1">
<TR>
<TD ALIGN="Center" VALIGN="Top" ROWSPAN="2">  <FONT SIZE="-1"><B>Borehole No.</B></FONT>
</TD>
<TD ALIGN="Center" VALIGN="Top" COLSPAN="3"><FONT SIZE="-1"><B>No. of
Monitoring Zones</B></FONT></TD>
