</P>
<P>2.19 This section addresses the various points made concerning the
establishment of baseline conditions (PE/FOE/5, paragraph 5.5; PE/FOE/4, section
5, paragraphs 7.7 and 8.5; PE/FOE/1, paragraph 9.7).
</P>
