<P><B>1. <A NAME="SUMMARY">SUMMARY</A>
</B>
</P>
<P> See <A HREF="nrx15s1s.htm"><B>PE/NRX/15/S1 SUMMARY</B></A>
</P>
<P><B>2. <A NAME="INTRODUCTION">INTRODUCTION</A>
</B>
</P>
<P>2.1 In this Supplementary Proof I comment on the Proofs of Evidence which
oppose the planning application for the RCF on the grounds that aspects of
safety assessment research and modelling have not been adequately addressed by
Nirex.  I include comments on the Proofs and the Evidence led by:
</P>
<TABLE BORDER="BORDER">
<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">
<TD WIDTH="50"></TD>
<TD WIDTH="50">i.</TD>
<TD>Dr Starmer (PE/CCC/5 for Cumbria County Council);</TD></TR>
<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">
<TD></TD>
<TD>ii.</TD>
<TD>Dr Salmon (PE/FOE/5 for Friends of the Earth) (paragraphs 4.20 to 4.26);</TD></TR>
<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">
<TD></TD>
<TD>iii.</TD>
