</P>
<P>NRX/16/8<BR>Hydraulic properties of the excavation-disturbed zone around
underground openings. C.D. Martin, E.T. Kozak, N.A. Chandler. In Proc. 45th
Canadian Geotechnical Conference, Toronto, October 26-28, 1992, pp 89:1-10.<BR>
</P>
