Excavation. R. Pusch. Int. J. Rock Mech. Min.Sci. &amp; Geomech. Abstr. Vol 26,
No 1, pp 79-83 1989.<BR>
</P>
<P>FOE/5/14<BR>Kelsall, P.C. Case, J.B. and C.R. Chabannes, 1984. Evaluation
of excavation-induced changes in rock permeability, Int. J. Rock. Mech. Sci &amp;
Geomech. Abstr. 21, 3, p123-135. <BR>
</P>
